Papandreou Says Greece to Have Primary Surplus in 2012

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-09-27T08:44:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/papandreou-says-greece-to-have-primary-surplus-in-2012.html
Greece  will achieve a primary
surplus next year, Prime Minister  George Papandreou  said.  “I’m confident that Greece will have a primary surplus in
2012,” Papandreou said in a speech to a BDI German industry
federation event in Berlin today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
